      "docs": "Secondary port for embedding computation. This track adds embed_batch (IN-08/AC-10): batch embedding of multiple CodeFragments in a single inference call, eliminating per-fragment CPU inference overhead for large corpora. Single-item embed is retained for other callers (OS-10). NOTE: embed_batch is declared ahead of implementation (catalogue-first TDDD); the type-signal for it will show as declared-not-found until the implementation lands.",
